! [[一]] || [[日]] || [[三]] || [[秋]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
===Etymology===
一 ''one'' + 日 ''day'' + 三 ''three'' + 秋 ''autumns''


===Idiom===
'''一日三秋''' (いちじつさんしゅう, ichijitsu sanshū)
# [[impatiently]]
# time dragging on


===Synonyms===
*[[一日千秋]]

[[Category:Japanese idioms|いちじつさんしゅう]]

