==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: (not seeing somebody for) one day (is like being apart for) three autumns

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' yī rì sān qiū)
# a single day apart seems like three years

===Synonyms===
*{{zh-ts|[[一日不見，如隔三秋]]|[[一日不见，如隔三秋]]}}

